osting comedy shows, premiering movies, haunted houses, talent shows, various cultural experiences and other fun community things.</p>\n<p>As a volunteer for the organization above, I acquired some community outreach skills. Since my school had several events per month for an entire academic school year, I learned pretty quickly how to promote events through tabling, creating flyers, and reaching out on social media for all of the campus events. In addition to promoting events, I also learned a bit about event planning, specifically accommodating for a large number of people and making it an inclusive and accessible space for all.</p>\n'),(350,211,'_vfb_field-35','<p>I am a full-time college student, however I hope to volunteer on a somewhat regular basis. Possibly able to commit to 6 or 7 hours per week at most.</p>\n<p>For spring term, I am available after 2:30 pm Mondays and Wednesdays, before 12 pm Tuesdays, and after 11 am on Fridays.</p>\n'),(351,211,'_vfb_field-36','Sunday, Monday, Tuesday, Wednesday, Friday, Saturday'),(352,211,'_vfb_field-37','Afternoon (12pm-4pm), Evening (4pm and after)'),(353,212,'_vfb_form_id','2'),(354,212,'_vfb_seq_num','2'),(355,212,'_vfb_entry_id','212'),(356,212,'vfbp-spam',''),(357,212,'_vfb_field-23','Shaay Gallagher-Starr'),(358,212,'_vfb_field-29','She/her/hers'),(359,212,'_vfb_field-30','No'),(360,212,'_vfb_field-31','Bisexual ciswoman'),(361,212,'_vfb_field-28','1974'),(362,212,'_vfb_field-25','(541) 255-9538'),(363,212,'_vfb_field-26','shaaygs@gmail.com'),(364,212,'_vfb_field-27','Email'),(365,212,'_vfb_field-32','<U>Donate Money</U> - every dollar counts!, <U>Donate Time</U> - to do whatever is needed (table an event, setup/tear-down, phone banking, door greeter, etc.), <U>Donate Skills</U> - do you have a special skill that you would like to offer? (painting, pod-casting, blogging, art, carpentry, fundraising, etc.)'),(366,212,'_vfb_field-33','<p>General support for</p>\n'),(367,212,'_vfb_field-41',''),(368,212,'_vfb_field