osave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(49,2,'2017-01-16 18:55:20','2017-01-17 02:55:20','This is a monthly social gathering for the trans-identified, gender diverse, gender questioning, AND for our allies. This is your opportunity to meet new folks in the area, visit, hang out in good company, and get to know each other in a relaxed social setting. There is NO cover charge to get in, and any donations made go directly to Trans*Ponder to support the community.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Each We/Us/Ours event is lightly facilitated by two Trans*Ponder group members. Activities may be offered during the event and you are welcome to participate or just be social! If you have questions or concerns during the event please seek out a facilitator or email the Trans*Ponder administrative team at </span><a href=\"mailto:admin@transponder.community\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">admin@transponder.community</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.</span>\r\n\r\n<b>Purpose / Goal:</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Hang out and socialize with gender diverse folks in a safe and inclusive public setting</span></li>\r\n 	<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">HAVE FUN!</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Age Limit: </strong>ALL AGES (though be aware this is an establishment where alcohol is consumed)\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://transponder.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/WUOFlyer-v2.0.pdf\">Download Event Flyer</a>','We/Us/Ours Trans/Gender Diverse Happy Hour','','publish','closed','closed','','weusours-transgender-diverse-happy-hour','','','2018-02-09 14:40:48','2018-02-09 22:40:48','',0,'http://transponder.community/?post_type=event&#038;p=49',0,'event','',0),(50,1,'2016-12-30 12:44:03','2016-12-30 20:44:03','<h2>Meetings</h2>\r\n[eo_events event_category=\"meetings\"]\r\n<h2>Recurring Events</h2>\r\n[eo_events event_category=\"recurring-events\"]\r\n<h2>Special Events</h2>\r\n[eo_even