meyer.com/topic/community-rewards-4\" style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-weight: bold\">Community Rewards Program</a> gives customers the opportunity to donate to a nonprofit of their choosing each time they shop at Fred Meyer. This means that once you associate Trans*Ponder to your Rewards Card account and go shopping Trans*Ponder will get a donation (quarterly) based on the accumulated spending of everyone who has signed up with the program. Pretty cool! This is a really easy and smart way to make regular donations without it ever coming out of your pocket or bank account. This program has no effect on the personal benefits you receive (Rewards Points, Rebates, and Fuel Points) from using your rewards card.\r\n\r\n<table style=\"margin-left: 50px; border: double darkblue; background-color: #e6f7ff;\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr style=\"border: 0px;\">\r\n<td style=\"border: 2px solid darkblue; background-color: #90bed5;\"><strong>Instructions for how to link Trans*Ponder to your Fred Meyer Rewards Card:</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"border: 0px;\">\r\n<td style=\"border: 0px;\">\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Go to <strong><a href=\"http://www.fredmeyer.com/communityrewards\" style=\"text-decoration: underline\">http://www.fredmeyer.com/communityrewards</a> </strong></li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Sign in</strong> to (or create) your account</li>\r\n 	<li>Click on the “<strong><a href=\"https://www.fredmeyer.com/account/communityrewards/enroll\"  style=\"text-decoration: underline\">Re-enroll or link your Rewards Card now</a></strong>” link</li>\r\n 	<li>Type “<strong>TransPonder</strong>” in the box that says Find Your Organization and click on <strong>Search</strong></li>\r\n 	<li>Click on the radio-button next to Trans*Ponder’s name to select it</li>\r\n 	<li>Click <strong>Enroll</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Voila! You’re done ????</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\nThat\'s it.  Trans*Ponder will now get a donation each time you shop at Fred Meyer. For program information and details check out the Community Rewards Program <a href=\"https://www.fredmeyer.com/topic/community-rewards-4\" style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-weight: bold\">HERE</a>.\r\n\r\nThank you so much for your consideration and support!!','Fred Meyer Community Rewards Program','','publish','closed','closed','','fredmeyer-rewards','','','2018-02-01 15:50:28','2018-02-01 23:50:28','',33,'http://transponder.community/?page_id=314',0,'page','',0),(315,2,'2018-02-01 14:27:18','2018-02-01 22:27:18','','FredMeyerTP','','inherit','open','closed','','fredmeyertp','','','2018-02-01 14:27:18','2018-02-01 22:27:18','',314,'http://transponder.community/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/FredMeyerTP.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(345,2,'2018-02-01 15:11:42','2018-02-01 23:11:42','<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-315\" src=\"http://transponder.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/FredMeyerTP.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"270\" />\r\n\r\n<h5>Did you know that each time you shop at <a href=\"https://www.fredmeyer.com/\">Fred Meyer</a> and use your rewards card you could be making a donation to Trans*Ponder?</h5>\r\n<BR>\r\nThe <a href=\"https://www.fredmeyer.com/topic/community-rewards-4\">Community Rewards Program</a> gives customers the opportunity to donate to a nonprofit of their choosing each time they shop at Fred Meyer. This means that once you associate Trans*Ponder to your Rewards Card account and go shopping Trans*Ponder will get a donation (quarterly) based on the accumulated spending of everyone who has signed up with the program. Pretty cool! This is a really easy and smart way to make regular donations without it ever coming out of your pocket or bank account. This program has no effect on the personal benefits you receive (Rewards Points, Rebates, and Fuel Points) from using your rewards card.\r\n\r\n<table style=\"margin-left: 50px; border: double darkblue; background-color: #e6f7ff;\">\r\n<tbody>\r\